  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Being a spy on an unfamiliar planet, anyone would have been greeted with hostility, but you were incredibly lucky! Trusting locals mistook you for a new neighbor and provided you with a house and a plot of land to live on. <br>         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/9ce8856208efc2a8a8e833509f8f8a00.avif?t=1773102252\" width=1444 height=410 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You'll have to help out the locals: learn their stories, make \"friends\" or even something more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/67b8f84e963096dc26d77d00c7132427.poster.avif?t=1773102252\" width=976 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/67b8f84e963096dc26d77d00c7132427.webm?t=1773102252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Win favour of the villagers, impress them with your achievements.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Become a champion fisherman by showing patience and wits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Engage in farming and grow various crops.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Descend and explore the long-abandoned dungeons that hide secrets of the island.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Show off your culinary skills by cooking flavourful dishes. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/0e9f62d6dc9eb70565c2cbd7c760bbdd.poster.avif?t=1773102252\" width=976 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/0e9f62d6dc9eb70565c2cbd7c760bbdd.webm?t=1773102252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What drew attention of the command to this planet? Is this really a paradise island, or is its allure merely a deceptive facade? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know your new friends better and find the one who really holds a threat to everyone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/db2066ffd8a4190ced9ec8f8c38c5ca9.avif?t=1773102252\" width=976 height=415 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Being a spy on an unfamiliar planet, anyone would have been greeted with hostility, but you were incredibly lucky! Trusting locals mistook you for a new neighbor and provided you with a house and a plot of land to live on. <br>         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/9ce8856208efc2a8a8e833509f8f8a00.avif?t=1773102252\" width=1444 height=410 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You'll have to help out the locals: learn their stories, make \"friends\" or even something more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/67b8f84e963096dc26d77d00c7132427.poster.avif?t=1773102252\" width=976 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/67b8f84e963096dc26d77d00c7132427.webm?t=1773102252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Win favour of the villagers, impress them with your achievements.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Become a champion fisherman by showing patience and wits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Engage in farming and grow various crops.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Descend and explore the long-abandoned dungeons that hide secrets of the island.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Show off your culinary skills by cooking flavourful dishes. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/0e9f62d6dc9eb70565c2cbd7c760bbdd.poster.avif?t=1773102252\" width=976 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/0e9f62d6dc9eb70565c2cbd7c760bbdd.webm?t=1773102252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What drew attention of the command to this planet? Is this really a paradise island, or is its allure merely a deceptive facade? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know your new friends better and find the one who really holds a threat to everyone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/db2066ffd8a4190ced9ec8f8c38c5ca9.avif?t=1773102252\" width=976 height=415 /></span></p>",
